et.jpg 2200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/POC-Tectal-Bike-Helmet-297x130.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/POC-Tectal-Bike-Helmet-800x351.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/POC-Tectal-Bike-Helmet-120x53.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/POC-Tectal-Bike-Helmet-768x337.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/POC-Tectal-Bike-Helmet-1536x674.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/POC-Tectal-Bike-Helmet-2048x899.jpg 2048w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>POC designed the Tectal helmet for aggressive trail riding and enduro racing with more coverage than a conventional mountain bike helmet, specifically with extended zones around the temples and back of the head. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>The unibody polycarbonate shell construction helps keep the weight down and it has a reinforced EPS liner. It showcases a wind-tunnel-tested ventilation system and the same aramid bridge system proven in the brand’s award-winning Trabec helmet.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Other features include an eye garage, a 360-degree adjustment system, and a RECCO reflector.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Check out all the <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreiclearq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fc%2Fbike-helmets%2Ff%2Fscd-deals\">bike helmet deals</a> in the sale. </p>\n\n\n<a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreiclearq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F232964%2Fpoc-tectal-bike-helmet\" target=\"_blank\">Shop Now</a>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>Five Ten Freerider Mountain Bike Shoes — </strong><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=cl&amp;mi=10248&amp;pw=293233&amp;ctc=brspreiclearq124&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F872539%2Ffive-ten-freerider-mountain-bike-shoes-mens\"><strong>Men’s </strong></a><strong>&amp; </strong><a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?